INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS.DESCRICAO-INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS:
The RRM Simulator supports:
. switch voice modeling and future implementation of switch data packet;
. modification of generic RRM algorithms, so proprietary algorithms can be tested;
. statistical funcionalities to generate random variables;
. a graphical interface, allowing management of multiple simulation runs;
. data import from PlaNet files;
. future implementation of other standards, such as IS-95, GSM or 3G.
